{
  "stem": "2226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they had-- before us was the Holland people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were in worse like me, because they didn't know the language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had I remember the mukluks, the wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you couldn't work in them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was very good them shoes, because you didn't freeze at your feet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So finally, Mengele stayed like that-- a little stick here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he picked out from our 1,000 men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He picked out I would say about 155, 160 people-- the young-- the youngest, the strongest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With me exactly, and I went where the mother is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't going by myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I come-- get  a kick in my back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I see a German at the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't stay here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went over there on the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That ?] with the life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] the other way [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lots of people were screaming they wanted to go over to the car with the red cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Always the red cross behind, always with the trucks on the front and on the back with the red cross, always.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the doctor poisoned himself, so we know a little bit what's happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got in in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got in-- it was nighttime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know and where right away, where-- where we went was right away with canes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They hit you with the sticks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You would never believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then we went over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stayed in that camp in a block, I think, I remember the wooden, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stayed over there till the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next morning we come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
